text: In this study, the percentages of animals with antibodies against H1N1pdm09 and H3N2 SIV were 26Á23% and 1Á57%, respectively, considering the 3000 samples tested. The percentages of seropositive herds for both viruses were 96Á6% and 13Á2%, respectively. The HI results per area and virus are summarized in Table 1 .
